 and utilized. Important for\neducators is how our low overhead production workflow was sustainable\nthroughout a busy semester.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 11 Oct 2021 20:41:25 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 13 Oct 2021 19:56:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-15"}
