, hence can directly inform binary\nevolution models. Finally, we comment on the potential to further characterise\nthese BH binaries through radial velocity measurements and observation of X-ray\ncounterparts.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 12 Oct 2021 13:15:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 17 Mar 2022 18:00:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-19"}
