ent with the Planck\n$\\Lambda$CDM best-fit $\\Omega_{\\rm c}h^{2} n_{\\rm s} = 0.116 \\pm 0.001$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 12 Oct 2021 15:56:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-06"}
